OL,6,FA driver who had downed nine beers and
OL,7,Fa shot before crashing into a teacher
OL,8,Fwho was walking home from the pub has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed.
OL,11,FThomas Sanigar, of Tiverton Street,
OL,12,FCleethorpes, had drunk seven pints of
OL,13,Flager, a pint of Guinness, a bottle of
OL,14,Flager and a shot at an event in
OL,15,FBeverley before getting behind the
OL,16,Fwheel of his BMW on 3 February.
OL,18,FHe was travelling at twice the 30mph
OL,19,Fspeed limit when he hit 30-year-old
OL,20,FAlex Ramsden, who had been out with a
OL,21,Ffriend and was walking home.
