OL,6,FA roadside breath test found he was
OL,7,Fmore than twice the drink drive limit.
OL,9,FSanigar pleaded guilty to causing
OL,10,Fdeath by dangerous driving at Grimsby
OL,11,FCrown Court.JIn a statement Alex's
OL,12,Ffather, Paul Ramsden told the court
OL,13,Fhis family's "whole world was crushed".
OL,15,FHe added: "My world is empty, a
OL,16,Ffeeling of total loss. All I have left
OL,17,Fof my beautiful boy is a picture hung
OL,18,Fon the wall. Alex is gone forever."
