OL,6,FHis mother Mum Elaine added: "I am in
OL,7,Fa bottomless pit with no way out, no
OL,8,Flight at the end of the tunnel.
OL,10,F"An irreparable chasm has opened up.
OL,11,FAlex was funny, highly-intelligent,
OL,12,Fcaring patient and loving."
OL,14,FSentencing Sanigar to nine years and
OL,15,Fnine months in prison, Judge John
OL,16,FThackray KC said Mr Ramsden's death
OL,17,Fwas "inevitable" after Sanigar got
OL,18,Fbehind the wheel.
