OL,6,F"It was a toxic combination of
OL,7,Fdangerous driving, highly impaired by
OL,8,Fthe consumption of alcohol and at
OL,9,Fgrossly excessive speed," he said.
OL,11,F"It ended a life and brought life-long
OL,12,Fgrief to his family."
OL,14,FIn a statement after the hearing, Mr
OL,15,FRamsden's family said: "Drinking and
OL,16,Fdriving destroys lives.
