OL,6,F"We should never have had to ensure
OL,7,Fthe heartbreak of losing Alex and the
OL,8,Fdevastation caused by the careless
OL,9,Factions of others. Nobody should have
OL,10,Fto go through this hell."
OL,12,FSgt Rob Mazingham, of Humberside
OL,13,FPolice, said: "Once again a
OL,14,Fcombination of excess speed and drink
OL,15,Fand the poor decision-making of a
OL,16,Fdriver, in this case Thomas Sanigar,
OL,17,Fhave led to the totally unnecessary
OL,18,Fand tragic death of an innocent
OL,19,Fpedestrian, Alex Ramsden.
